questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you redesign my existing wordpress website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can redesign an existing WordPress website based on your instructions. Please feel free to message me with your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you customize my WordPress website according to my specific requirements?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I offer fully customized design services tailored to your brand identity and preferences. Whether you need a unique layout, custom features, or integration with third-party tools, I'll ensure that your website reflects your vision perfectly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after the website is launched?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer free 30 days of support after the launch of your website. If you encounter any issues or need assistance with updates or maintenance, you can reach out to me, and I'll be happy to help.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website easily?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Your website will be fully editable! You can very easily add text & images to all pages with a click! You can edit e-commerce products, their images, descriptions & prices and add unlimited pages and posts too. No programming skills are required! :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide hosting and domains?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Unfortunately, No, I do not provide. You will need to provide the domain and hosting.
